Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們把意誌與努力都無法改變的機緣稱為運
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.72,0:00:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現遊弋的元神靈 對其進行追查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果幸與不幸都是由運所主宰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們是會選擇任其擺布呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是會為了得到強運而奮鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者是 與其抗爭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:51.27,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみが宿った眼に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:51.27,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我悲傷的瞳孔中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:53.63,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映しだす　君のmotion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:53.63,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映出了你閃動的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:57.77,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思いが流れてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:57.77,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思憶潮水般湧來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:01.15,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求められ選択した
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:01.15,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我選擇了他們想要的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.70,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その答えは　そうfusion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.70,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可在這選擇的作用下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:07.70,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛みが導く先にある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:07.70,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現的卻是痛苦的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.70,0:01:12.98,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黒い闇　迫っても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.70,0:01:12.98,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是在黑暗面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:17.94,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑顔をいつもくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:17.94,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容始終依舊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:23.13,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光を護るため
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:23.13,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了守衛光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.13,0:01:30.15,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君と今　ひとつになれる…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.13,0:01:30.15,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我此刻與你融為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:35.98,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追いつけないほどの力　手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:35.98,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得讓人望塵莫及的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:40.50,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風を切って貫いてゆけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:40.50,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後去穿透烈風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:45.64,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰を信じてる…？　通じ合えたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:45.64,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能相互信任理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:50.50,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡起こせる　何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:50.50,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能不斷創造奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:56.42,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真実いつか　見えるから…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:56.42,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能最終發現真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎麼還在睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我做了慶太愛吃的豬排三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保持營養均衡 還做了蔬菜三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 我會吃完的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣了 別遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由朋友的媽媽似乎被倒車的車撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過幸好倒車的速度不快…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話今晚來我家吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 不過今晚我已經有約了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定要來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人的好意是沈重的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一個人的羈絆越深 就越容易左右他的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對的 自己的人生也會深陷其中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:04.93,i,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 01 「三位一在」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸運 伊吹你也遲到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼幸運的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我一個不就太顯眼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幫您把便當熱一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近撞大運了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 中了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說要邀我去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我已經和靜說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再約你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我說說罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快到座位上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田也遲到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 笠井沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是轉校了 還是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢你 只是感冒了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最近不是經常發生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 靜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我 理佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹 一起去卡拉OK吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該有優惠券的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我今天要幫鄰居看小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 下次一定去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要只看不買
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會取消了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正準備去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才沖繩地區發生了輕度地震，強度為…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉面好了 蛋是我請的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直勞您關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一號線馬上入站 請不要越出黃線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎您光臨由K-ON MART贊助的GSD現場演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人怎麼跟座山似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵 理佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到別處去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像妹妹的弟弟倒是有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個穿紅衣服的跟你長得一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙生幻象果真存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:08:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵 你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是模特公司的星探 能耽誤您點時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 不是已經死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說她是媽媽的雙生幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是撞人逃逸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像當場就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還那麼年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了嗎 我都打了好幾遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天做了你喜歡吃的蛋黃醬飯團…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…扣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天的記憶總是揮之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽在和她相遇後的隔天便去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹你真好運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的傳單？怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上還有兩個跟自己長得一樣的人的傳說是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們看到了和理佐一模一樣的的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙生幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩不煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵 你要註意下安全啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會真的相信雙生幻象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 但只怕萬一嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在為我擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在高興什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞蛋拉面好了 叉燒算是我請的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 慶太都是熟客了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光…臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我一碗拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你有錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在耍我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這連杯面也買不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃不了拉面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請我吃這麼貴的東西真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那慶太就由我請客吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我爸也差不多該匯錢來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽因為之前的一場交通意外…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你知道雙生幻象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上還有兩個跟自己長得一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人看見了自己的雙生幻象便會死去 我媽媽便是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙生幻象不過是空想的傳說罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實存在的是三位一在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是維持容量平衡的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由三個長得一樣的人共同分攤命運
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是兩個填補者撞見了 依照法則
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人都會因為疾病或是事故什麼的從世上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而剩下的第三人即根源則會吸收掉兩人的運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜 你母親不幸是個填補者而非根源
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵 你幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對個這麼小的女孩出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵 你有聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真耐打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:15:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是元神靈 看來用不著留手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次來個對心直擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 快報警
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個人類 少礙手礙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易有人請我吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此重要的一碗拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒？就憑你個遊弋的元神靈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少瞧不起人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說想嘗嘗倔強的元神靈的容量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無奈命令卻是活捉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到了嗎 已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 把你給卷進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫小黑 是元神靈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是普尼普尼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元神…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉面 那麼多湯都浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉浪費了您請的拉面 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普尼普尼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去殺掉哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 慶太愛吃的菜肉卷馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青梅竹馬也沒必要做到這個份上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼話啊 我不管你就連飯也不好好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太之所以不願和人親近是因為他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是覺得自己帶來的不幸害死了他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.11,p,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一條新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確發生了很多不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:01.23,p,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京都內某建築工地發生意外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你媽媽身上 你的朋友身上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:04.74,p,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路過的三人不幸遇難
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.05,p,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的姓名是 山田理佐 17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:13.12,p,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田村和夫 45歲 山崎明 27…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵 伊吹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 嚇到你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有更令人吃驚的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由今早看見了個跟我長得一樣的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年紀也差不多 就好像有另一個我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 真由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有女孩子被車撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快叫救護車
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子不是根源
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經覺得如果命中註定 也只好認了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能做的只有盡量避免牽連別人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可如果註定了的命運如此荒唐 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:07.05,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつしか朝を迎え
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:07.05,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺已至清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:12.15,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凍てつく躰溶けて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:12.15,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵硬的身體開始恢復溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:18.27,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覚めた記憶で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:18.27,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我整理思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.43,0:22:24.00,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早すぎた死を還して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.43,0:22:24.00,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕了再度襲來的睡意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:29.99,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲たちの鳴く聲も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:29.99,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲兒低鳴的聲音消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:36.00,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥たちの舞う羽音にも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:36.00,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥兒展翅的聲音也沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:42.00,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音を亡くした　白き涸れ地に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:42.00,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬籟俱靜　一片慘白的荒蕪大地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:48.10,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あふれる彩を　そそいでいく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:48.10,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地被陽光染上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:51.87,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あざやかに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:51.87,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絢麗的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.05,0:23:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜各位 你們已經吸收了大量的運
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到屬於被選上了的人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:12.06,o,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode 「契約」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起你們就是主根源了
